4%D7%99%D7%A8%D7%99_%D7%91%D7%9E%D7%A1%D7%99%D7%91%D7%AA_%D7%94%D7%97%D7%A0%D7%95%D7%9B%D7%94_%D7%91%D7%A1%D7%99%D7%93%D7%A0%D7%99\" title=\"פיגוע הירי במסיבת החנוכה בסידני\">הפיגוע במסיבת חנוכה בסידני</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/%D7%AA%D7%A9%D7%A4%22%D7%95\" title=\"תשפ&quot;ו\">תשפ\"ו</a>)\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413091607\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: [show‐toc]\nCPU time usage: 0.134 seconds\nReal time usage: 2.601 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 402/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6224/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1303/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 6/100\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3854/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.060/7 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5877760/52428800 bytes\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00% 1830.016      1 -total\n 58.05% 1062.343      6 תבנית:הערה\n 10.49%  191.889      2 תבנית:קישור_שבור\n 10.33%  188.958      1 תבנית:פיגועי_טרור\n  9.63%  176.173      1 תבנית:הערות_שוליים\n  8.50%  155.509      1 תבנית:מקור\n  7.51%  137.355      1 תבנית:ניווט\n  2.90%   53.057      8 תבנית:*\n  1.32%   24.173      1 תבנית:חב&quot;ד_אינפו\n  0.86%   15.686      1 תבנית:ה\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key chabadped_1-infopedia_:pcache:idhash:13187-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413091607 and revision id 818160. Rendering was triggered because: diff-page\n -->\n</div>"
